text: Magnús Brynjólfsson (5 June 1923 - 6 December 1976) was an Icelandic alpine skier. He competed in two events at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:1976 deaths Magnús Brynjólfsson Magnús Brynjólfsson Category:Alpine skiers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Magnús Brynjólfsson
